        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/20/22",
        "text": [
          "٢٠. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): أَقِيلُوا ذَوِي الْمُرُوءَاتِ عَثَرَاتِهِمْ فَمَا يَعْثُرُ مِنْهُمْ عَاثِرٌ إِلَّا وَيَدُهُ بِيَدِ اللهِ يَرْفَعُهُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "20. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Forgive the shortcomings of people of virtue and honor because when they fall into error Allāh raises them up."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
